<DOC>
<DOCNO>GH950309-000117</DOCNO>
<DOCID>GH950309-000117</DOCID>
<DATE>950309</DATE>
<HEADLINE>School to close</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>4</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>979484928</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
CRAWFORDTON House at Moniaive, the largest private school in Dumfries
and Galloway, is to close in the summer because of falling pupil
numbers. The 55-year-old preparatory school was started in response to a
request by parents in Glasgow who wanted a school for their children
well away from the city because of bombing raids.
</TEXT>
