<TEXT>
* A Danish policeman, believing himself to be under fire, shot at
three divers wading ashore early today at the airport hydrofoil terminal
in Copenhagen, a few miles from the conference centre.
Deputy Police Commissioner Annemette Moeller said police had searched
for the mysterious frogmen but no trace of them had been found.
She said police were taking the incident seriously but ruled out the
possibility of a guerrilla attack on the heavily-guarded
summit.--Reuter.
</TEXT>
