<HEADLINE>Briton mugged</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>8</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>979484945</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
JOHANNESBURG: A 74-year-old British woman tourist was shot in both
legs during a mugging in the centre of Johannesburg yesterday. Police
said officers had arrested a man trying to rob her as she lay bleeding
on the pavement. The woman, who has not been named, was said to be in
stable condition in hospital.
