<TEXT>
DETECTIVE Constables Alan Kidd, 41, and Bob Gordon, 34, have raised
#4500 through events including golf, swimming, and a dance, to buy
medical equipment, toys, a television, and a video for the children's
ward in Dundee Royal Infirmary.
